[h3 id=Overview 
	" Overview
	$LF
]h3
[ul 
	[li 
		" Aims to highlight and preserve TAS content showcased in an event setting.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Runs that are incapable of being independently sync verified are allowed.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Event publications cannot be obsoleted.
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[h3 id=TechnicalRequirements 
	" Technical requirements
	$LF
]h3
[ul 
	[li 
		" Submissions must include a rehostable video of the event in question.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" All contributors to an event run must be properly attributed, and any objections raised by contributors must be taken into account.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Multi-game events must be split by run and submitted individually.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" An input file matching the game and console must be provided, though it does not have to accurately reflect the run.
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[h3 id=EventRequirements 
	" Event requirements
	$LF
]h3
[ul 
	[li 
		" The run must be showcased in a way that isn't otherwise publishable.
		$LF
		[ul 
			[li 
				" Publishable event runs 
				(__wikiLink|displaytext=will be properly published to their appropriate class|href=/2513M)
				".
				$LF
			]li
			[li 
				" Showcases of already published runs will be treated as commentary for that run, unless the showcase is transformative enough to warrant a separate publication.
			]li
		]ul
	]li
]ul
